{"tid":2107853,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"瑞和街市政大廈失守  患者(#1512)曾至大家樂、龍慶堂(有先人牌位)","createTime":"2020-07-14T07:02:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T13:12:51.000Z","uid":7439,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"061c32d3963ff281e7a4f830b188a263eb750424","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/4854045/org/a4652c85d868227f61b7119c69498035.jpg/a6juf9g_xqmbNEw_LQwL7tB22636pwm_qkAMMapADDE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F4854045%2Forg%2Fa4652c85d868227f61b7119c69498035.jpg%2Fa6juf9g_xqmbNEw_LQwL7tB22636pwm_qkAMMapADDE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=333b669b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#1512  7月13日<br />\n51歲 香港女子 屬#1492朋友。<br />\n<blockquote>觀塘 翠屏南邨翠樂樓 1512<br />\n油尖旺 太子道康寧大廈地下 A 及B 舖 大家樂 06/07/2020 1512<br />\n深水埗 龍慶堂 06/07/2020 1512<br />\n油尖旺 旺角中心第 1 座 07/07/2020 1315, 1512<br />\n<span class=\"red\">觀塘 瑞和街市政大廈 11/07/2020 1512</span><br />\n觀塘 翠屏北商場 12/07/2020 1512</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n#1492 7月13日 <br />\n66歲 香港男子，患者無外遊紀錄，為#1512朋友。被送往屯門醫院接受治療。<br />\n<blockquote>黃大仙 竹園邨鵬程苑 1492</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n#1315 7月8日 <br />\n55歲 香港男子，任職計程車司機，本身有糖尿和腎病，需要洗肚，沒有接觸確診者。<br />\n<blockquote>報稱7月2日開始咳嗽，在入急症室時出現發燒，亦表示已咳嗽一星期和有氣促，醫生檢查時發現含氧量和血壓偏低，給予高濃度氧氣聞後進度不理想，故已插喉用呼吸機協助呼吸，目前含氧量有所好轉，但仍要用呼吸機，被送往伊利沙伯醫院加護病房接受治療，未知是否曾到新發茶餐廳。張竹君補充，其太太(#1332)和女兒(#1331)有不適，是確診個案。<br />\n黃大仙 鳳德邨碧鳳樓 1315<br />\n油尖旺 旺角中心第 1 座 07/07/2020 1315, 1512</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lunghingtong.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/6040B1AB-3BBC-43FF-BAAE-B0B104A8C695.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lunghingtong.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F6040B1AB-3BBC-43FF-BAAE-B0B104A8C695.jpg&h=877a02c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.lunghingtong.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/09/%E5%85%88%E4%BA%BA%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E5%A3%87%E7%A5%9E%E4%BD%8D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lunghingtong.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F09%2F%25E5%2585%2588%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25B4%2580%25E5%25BF%25B5%25E5%25A3%2587%25E7%25A5%259E%25E4%25BD%258D.jpg&h=ae63a811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3066bc1485913f51653798837a2fac6746f41258","tid":2107853,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"觀塘撚冇得買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1312dd9fede6115bba5e373c94d29ce976b7681d","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:03:26.000Z","msg":"一個好消息 一個壞消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Vv8gtt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Vv8gtt.jpg&h=16e17b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九東初選 瑞和雙雄(梁凱晴+ 李嘉達)全勝！！！！！！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2106848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2106848</a>"},{"pid":"1f4515b6648cabedaeeffbedca448cfa1fbb8fec","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:03:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o2isvG9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo2isvG9.jpg&h=e1cf664f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佛堂義工(#98)曾到觀塘藥房中醫求診  瑞和街599C十面埋伏<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1910190\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1910190</a><br />\n<br />\n觀塘舊樓單位爆屎渠3天 屎水浸走廊 正面播毒瑞和街市政大廈<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1863815\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1863815</a><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎】流鶯猖獗瑞和街惹播毒隱憂 街坊恐引社區爆發<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1859154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1859154</a>"},{"pid":"40b6c9436d486f77816873407292376f262a2ab4","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3066bc1485913f51653798837a2fac6746f41258","tid":2107853,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"觀塘撚冇得買餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"觀塘食肆被罰暫停營業十四天<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  觀塘一食肆經營者因食物室不潔、在露天地方貯存及配製食物，以及沒有妥善貯存未加掩蓋的食物，屢次違反《食物業規例》，被食物環境衞生署（食環署）署長暫時吊銷牌照十四天。<br />\n <br />\n  該食肆名為「龍記燒味飯店」，位於觀塘瑞和街50─68號地下G鋪，由今日（七月七日）至七月二十日須暫停營業。<br />\n <br />\n  食環署發言人說：「有關食肆經營者因上述違例事項，於二○一八年九月至去年七月期間三次被法庭定罪，共罰款五千七百元。本署亦根據違例記分制記下持牌人十五分，食肆因此須停牌十四天。」<br />\n <br />\n  有關持牌人亦因沒有妥善貯存未加掩蓋的食物，二○一八年七月及二○一九年三月兩次被法庭定罪，共罰款四千七百元，因而被記下十五分，食肆二○一九年十月被暫時吊銷牌照七天。"},{"pid":"2cf3347394da43e444da50954a154b6af3f8eab8","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:09:43.000Z","msg":"OK，我笠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌哂你哋老母 康體通(炒場師)恢復服務+瑞和街活動室重開 無人講？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2026075\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2026075</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>康文署公共服務最新安排<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  康樂及文化事務署（康文署）今日（七月十三日）宣布，因應2019冠狀病毒病的最新情況，有需要採取進一步限制措施，減少社交接觸。康文署將於七月十五日（星期三）起暫停開放所有較早前重開的康樂和文化場地／設施，直至另行通告；同時亦取消七月份餘下的所有康樂、體育及文化活動。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ce887ba46daca00b5e87b8e367fd71adfccb4b2b","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T10:56:29.000Z","msg":"第1884號患者、34歲女子，居於翠竹花園2座，她在發病期間也到過多處，包括：本月14日到過香港朗廷酒店、元朗形點二期茶木；19日到過牛頭角公廁浴室及瑞和街市政大廈。"},{"pid":"92de51ec238a6741a4b51afc15de65a469f251e9","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:05:00.000Z","msg":"觀塘 瑞和街市政大廈 19/07/2020<br />\n1512, 1672, 1802,1884<br />\n<br />\n#1512 51歲 香港女子，居於觀塘翠屏南邨翠樂樓，與#1492是朋友。患者7月6日開始喉嚨痛、咳嗽及頭痛，被送往聯合醫院接受治療。<br />\n<br />\n#1672 (穩定) 46 歲 男<br />\n第 #1705 宗個案患者的兒子，過往健康良好，無外遊記錄，7 月 12 日開始咳嗽及頭痛。<br />\n<br />\n#1802 女士39歲.<br />\n慈雲山中心薀莎餐廳群組的廚師<br />\n<br />\n#1884 34歲女子<br />\n居於翠竹花園2座，她在發病期間也到過多處，包括：本月14日到過香港朗廷酒店、元朗形點二期茶木；19日到過牛頭角公廁浴室及瑞和街市政大廈。"},{"pid":"37390a3cc1ab8a71dd975a50dd6f7e7363b4dd97","tid":2107853,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"瑞和街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48e963a91f2dd7bc4ec822d4018bcc0031e26086","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37390a3cc1ab8a71dd975a50dd6f7e7363b4dd97","tid":2107853,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"瑞和街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/115822919_582626755955448_3090732261498380604_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_ohc=Mbm_MzcSPn0AX_DByTK&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=b12f090f4cdbcd5e613ce1a2dd8fd39d&amp;oe=5F3E1C19\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F115822919_582626755955448_3090732261498380604_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_ohc%3DMbm_MzcSPn0AX_DByTK%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3Db12f090f4cdbcd5e613ce1a2dd8fd39d%26oe%3D5F3E1C19&h=47851c49&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3defc73c85c372cb30da75a7c5d3ea1e5ab559bc","tid":2107853,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"咁佢自己有冇位"},{"pid":"559cb3a74356c106a748f335c3b10d5444381092","tid":2107853,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3defc73c85c372cb30da75a7c5d3ea1e5ab559bc","tid":2107853,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T11:12:48.000Z","msg":"咁佢自己有冇位"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T13:12:51.000Z",